ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:16:59.000Z","msg":"以為自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中三已經話我喺屋企住係浪費佢地錢<br />\n做嘢又問我拎家用 放工又比說話我聽"},{"pid":"cdd8b86a1414994eff7d988f49757cf040412d1a","tid":1068941,"uid":118211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd67c738f07623732121d8ae0b3829f23995e4c6","tid":1068941,"uid":240665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:58:20.000Z","msg":"呀媽成日都講單單打打嘅說話<br />\n成日話 唔係我你連屋都冇得住<br />\n你有能力咪自己出去租劏房住囉<br />\n屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />業都未畢邊有錢出去住<br />\n我知係我廢係我冇骨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人屋企都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸 絲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:55:18.000Z","msg":"以為同一個老母講嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd0c5816d659292421b2f68ee766d937127fe36","tid":1068941,"uid":94652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"真心好灰"},{"pid":"c4db964ccc718dcf692157272ba283a591f8b527","tid":1068941,"uid":144848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:40:45.000Z","msg":"我老母咪係咁囉<br />\n由我細細個開始就無所事事<br />\n成日喺屋企拗爛腳<br />\n因為我呀爸同佢離左婚<br />\n成日叫我問我老豆拎錢，<br />\n但佢明明有做野<br />\n到我大個家用一蚊都唔出，啲嘢全部要我比<br />\n我之前同佢嘈交，我話冇呀媽好似你咁<br />\n你知唔知佢同我講啲咩啊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢叫我下世投胎投好啲</span><br />\n我永遠都會記得你點對我<br />\n多謝你比左我呢個勇氣，自己搬出去住<br />\n唔撚洗再受9你啲氣，八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}